### Create Resource (with JSON, no file)
POST http://localhost:5000/resource-api/resource
Cookie: token=YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "author" : "YOUR_USER_ID_HERE",
    "title" : "Calculus Chapter 1 Notes",
    "description" : "Complete notes covering limits and continuity",
    "content" : "Limits describe the value a function approaches...",
    "fileType" : "NOTE",
    "subject" : "Mathematics",
    "semester" : 3,
    "tags" : ["calculus", "limits"]
}

### Get Own Resources
GET http://localhost:5000/resource-api/resources

### Get Resource by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/resource-api/resource/RESOURCE_ID_HERE

### Update Resource
PUT http://localhost:5000/resource-api/resource
Cookie: token=YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "_id" : "RESOURCE_ID_HERE",
    "title" : "Calculus Chapter 1 Notes (Updated)",
    "description" : "Updated notes covering limits, continuity, and derivatives"
}

### Soft Delete Resource
PATCH http://localhost:5000/resource-api/resource/delete/RESOURCE_ID_HERE

### Restore Resource
PATCH http://localhost:5000/resource-api/resource/restore/RESOURCE_ID_HERE
